description:
Something incredibly important that people agree on? Let's do it!

Make a comment to the FCC by clicking "express" here: https://www.fcc.gov/ecfs/search/proceedings?q=name:((17-108)) (you'll have to add the two closing parentheses to the url yourself because youtube's automatic link-making function has a bug, apparently)

Want to call your representative but don't know how? http://whoismyrepresentative.com/

A pretty good site about it all: https://www.battleforthenet.com/

The bulk of this video is from 2014, with a revised beginning and ending
